{"tid":335262,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[javascript] 點解AddEventListener 失效?","createTime":"2017-07-25T12:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T22:45:23.000Z","uid":65030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb52aaa44ba9714e93bb97ed7e7b3b1c0e7576d4","tid":335262,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:30:23.000Z","msg":"document.write(&quot;&lt;div id='timer'&gt;0&lt;/div&gt;&quot;);<br />\n\t\tvar counter;<br />\n\t\tvar status=false;<br />\n\t\tfunction $(id){<br />\n\t\t\treturn document.getElementById(id);<br />\n\t\t}<br />\n\t\tfunction second(){<br />\n\t\t\tvar acc=parseInt($(&quot;timer&quot;).innerHTML)+1;<br />\n\t\t\t$(&quot;timer&quot;).innerHTML=acc;<br />\n\t\t}<br />\n\t\tfunction ontimer(){<br />\n\t\t\tif(status==false){<br />\n\t\t\t\tstatus=true;<br />\n\t\t\t\tcounter=setInterval(&quot;second()&quot;,1000);<br />\n\t\t\t}<br />\n\t\t\telse{<br />\n\t\t\t\tstatus=false;<br />\n\t\t\t\tclearInterval(counter);<br />\n\t\t\t}<br />\n\t\t}<br />\n\t\tvar timer=$(&quot;timer&quot;);<br />\n\ttimer.addEventListener(&quot;click&quot;, ontimer, false);<br />\n<br />\n點解我咁寫, 禁落去無反應?"},{"pid":"30ea0fa095f0123d599053a4811644636102285b","tid":335262,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"但係用onclick就無事"},{"pid":"be73688acacbc4936ccdaac9d0b406a21f84a19a","tid":335262,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5b86ae704ba5b331a9e917c7ec4b00a1372618","tid":335262,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"setinterval係pass function, pass string 我覺得會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d317fe06f60042bddd51f668b616c643264b322b","tid":335262,"uid":20840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"咩course"},{"pid":"8219abd54164a34cb97126f8a7d7d454a40a89bb","tid":335262,"uid":20840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:37:57.000Z","msg":"試下body onload加timer.addEventListener(&quot;click&quot;, ontimer, false);"},{"pid":"172c5e58144edc3b0f94d1f48776805989490727","tid":335262,"uid":69481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:41:48.000Z","msg":"問題應該係status 度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係debugger 行完你啲code , status 會變左String type<br />\n所以 status == false 會return false"},{"pid":"9d3fa02f8cf192159f5bdcac1e9948eb4076e45b","tid":335262,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下body onload加timer.addEventListener(&quot;click&quot;, ontimer, false);</blockquote><br />\n唔得, 我覺得係TRUE同FALSE的問題, 我加左幾句console.log測試過:<br />\n一開頭係status=false;<br />\n但係佢完全入唔到IF個STATEMENT入面"},{"pid":"2d56b64ebd8681509502a299e49142e67cd3b0a4","tid":335262,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問題應該係status 度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係debugger 行完你啲code , status 會變左String type<br />\n所以 status == false 會return false</blockquote><br />\n點解無LALA會變左String type?"},{"pid":"d01e24d81c0e096d2bf2d25275f679dff7666f22","tid":335262,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:47:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/s5170gvw/6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjsfiddle.net%2Fs5170gvw%2F6%2F&d=ammElTl8ef0XgIZwl6iYvzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=6f2a2f7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://jsfiddle.net/s5170gvw/6/</a>"},{"pid":"aecf144e8f80c30bfda7116c3af57bfed04cdb67","tid":335262,"uid":1573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問題應該係status 度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係debugger 行完你啲code , status 會變左String type<br />\n所以 status == false 會return false</blockquote><br />\n點解無LALA會變左String type?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/3485986\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fa%2F3485986&d=ammElTl8ef0XgIZwl6iYvzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9f3d520a\" target=\"_blank\">https://stackoverflow.com/a/3485986</a><br />\nin Chrome, window (the global object) has a status property, which for some reason Chrome seems to be referring to instead of your status var. Renaming status to anything else, say, myStatus, will give you the results you expect."},{"pid":"34d67a410034a66637449c7f84481156e4db4693","tid":335262,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:50:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>問題應該係status 度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係debugger 行完你啲code , status 會變左String type<br />\n所以 status == false 會return false</blockquote><br />\n點解無LALA會變左String type?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/3485986\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fa%2F3485986&d=ammElTl8ef0XgIZwl6iYvzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9f3d520a\" target=\"_blank\">https://stackoverflow.com/a/3485986</a><br />\nin Chrome, window (the global object) has a status property, which for some reason Chrome seems to be referring to instead of your status var. Renaming status to anything else, say, myStatus, will give you the results you expect.</blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTHX巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73670ef97389ec9467d67a24d911491e771c8b60","tid":335262,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:07:37.000Z","msg":"包佢落FUNCTIO 然後用'use strict';<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/s5170gvw/7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjsfiddle.net%2Fs5170gvw%2F7%2F&d=ammElTl8ef0XgIZwl6iYvzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=eb1b368c\" target=\"_blank\">https://jsfiddle.net/s5170gvw/7/</a>"},{"pid":"afebba5651587f54df32479ad0c54440525071e3","tid":335262,"uid":108937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:30:29.000Z","msg":"寫法太有趣了吧？巴打跟咩tutorial 學緊？好似好舊wor d 野"},{"pid":"787782faf53599cc5873551ad57d600522a7fcab","tid":335262,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫法太有趣了吧？巴打跟咩tutorial 學緊？好似好舊wor d 野</blockquote><br />\n上網左搵右搵的，有咩tutorial 好推介"}]}